data.description: Wonderful family home with a large yard centrally located to shopping, schools and medical facilities. This 3-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom with an additional bonus room that could function as another bedroom is move in ready. With an open kitchen and dining room that flows into the living area this home gives a feeling of being a lot larger. The beautiful tree shade yard and covered back patio will provide the perfect area for outdoor entertaining. Take advantage of the opportunity to see this home today!
